## Org & DevOps

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Local Source] -->|deploy| B[Dev Sandbox]
    B -->|DevOps Center| C[Staging]
    C -->|Promote| D[Production]
```

All metadata changes go through DevOps Center. Never deploy directly to production.

## Key Commands

| Command                                                 | Description                    |
| ------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| `sf project deploy start --target-org {dev}`            | Deploy metadata to dev sandbox |
| `sf project deploy start --target-org {dev} --dry-run`  | Validate without deploying     |
| `sf project deploy preview --target-org {dev}`          | Preview what would deploy      |
| `sf project retrieve preview --target-org {dev}`        | Preview what changed in org    |
| `sf flow scan --directory force-app/main/default/flows` | Scan flows for issues          |

